lead_paragraph: They teamed up for a carpool karaoke video. They planted their flag in Brazil. And when the Olympics are done, they'll be remembered as the latest in a long line of U.S. swimming powerhouses.

headline.main: So Much for the Dire Predictions of US Swimming Flop in Rio
